name: Empty World (Jellybean)
description:
Made in 3 hours for trijam.

I just about ran out of time, there's a bug which will let you drive indefinately to pick up fuel even when the tanks empty. Finding it is kinda cool though.

I also didn't manage to implement obstacles to destroy the car, or consequences for the decisions you make. Without obstacles, there's not much of a fight between answering the questions and steering the car, which was the whole point of the game!
